regex.expres:
#$pyFunction def GetLSProData(page_data,Cookie_Jar,m): import requests, re, urllib
url1= 'http://agenda.superligatv.com/sky2.html' source = requests.get(url1).text fid = re.findall('fid="(.*?)"', source)[0]
url2 = 'http://fut.superligatv.com/' + fid + '.php' headers = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (X11 Linux i686 rv:42.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/42.0 Iceweasel/42.0','Referer': url1} source2 = requests.get(url2, headers = headers).text
url3 =re.findall("src='(.*?)'", source2)[0] headers = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (X11 Linux i686 rv:42.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/42.0 Iceweasel/42.0','Referer': 'http://fut.superligatv.com/'} source3 = requests.get(url3, headers = headers).text part1= re.findall('var.*?=\["(.*?)"', source3)[0] part2= re.findall('stream/","/(.*?)","(.*?)","(.*?)\\"', source3)
pageUrl = 'http://www.shidurlive.com/stream/' + part1 + '/' + part2[0][0] + part2[0][1] + part2[0][2].replace('\\','') source4 = requests.get(pageUrl, headers = headers).text escape= re.findall("'file', unescape\('(.*?)'", source4)[0] playpath = urllib.unquote(escape) rtmp = re.findall("'streamer', '(.*?)'", source4)[0]
return rtmp + ' playpath=' + playpath + ' pageUrl=' + pageUrl

regex.expres: #$pyFunction import requests, re, base64 def GetLSProData(page_data,Cookie_Jar,m,url = 'http://miplayer.net/embedplayer.php?width=640&height=480&id=ibrodtv21&autoplay=true&strech=exactfit'): headers = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/51.0.2704.103 Safari/537.36', 'Referer': 'http://www.ibrod.tv/embed.php?chan=sp28&width=640&height=480'} source = requests.get(url, headers=headers) chid = re.findall('miplayer.*?channel.*?id=(.*?)"', source.text)[0] curl = re.findall('curl = "(.*?)"', source.text)[0] rtmp = base64.b64decode(curl) GETtoken = re.findall('getJSON.*"(.*file.*?)"', source.text)[0] url2 = GETtoken headers2 = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/51.0.2704.103 Safari/537.36', 'Referer': url, 'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest'} source2 = requests.get(url2, headers = headers2) token = re.findall('"token":"(.*?)"', source2.text)[0] playSXurl = rtmp + ' swfUrl=http://cdn.ibrod.tv/player/jwplayer.flash.swf token=' + token + ' timeout=15 live=true swfVfy=1 pageUrl=http://miplayer.net/embedplayer.php?width=640&height=480&id=' + chid + '&autoplay=true&strech=exactfit' return playSXurl
